Order Confirmation

Hello <%= @user.name %>,

Thank you for your order! We've received your order and it's being processed.

ORDER DETAILS
=============
Order Number: <%= @order.order_number %>
Order Date: <%= @order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>
Status: <%= @order.status.capitalize %>
Total Amount: ₦<%= number_with_precision(@order.total_price, precision: 2) %>
Outlet: <%= @outlet_type.capitalize %>

<% if @order.respond_to?(:sephcocco_pharmacy_products) || @order.respond_to?(:sephcocco_restaurant_products) || @order.respond_to?(:sephcocco_lounge_products) %>
ORDER ITEMS
==========
<% products = @order.sephcocco_pharmacy_products || @order.sephcocco_restaurant_products || @order.sephcocco_lounge_products %>
<% products.each do |product| %>
- <%= product.name %> (Qty: <%= product.quantity %>) - ₦<%= number_with_precision(product.price, precision: 2) %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

WHAT'S NEXT?
============
- We'll notify you when your order is being prepared
- You'll receive updates on your order status  
- We'll send you tracking information once your order is dispatched

If you have any questions about your order, please contact our support team.

